headline: Match Group Promotes Hesam Hosseini to Chief Operating Officer; Gary Swidler to Step Down as President
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) today announced the promotion of Hesam Hosseini to Chief Operating Officer, effective April 1. After a decade in senior leadership roles at the company, Gary Swidler will step down as President on that date and continue as an advisor to the company until July 4, 2025, as part of a thoughtfully planned transition.
